Package model

Class EntertainmentProvider

Object
model.User
model.EntertainmentProvider
public class EntertainmentProvider
extends User
EntertainmentProvider is a user of the application, who represents an organisation that hosts Events. They can browse events, create new events, cancel their own events and see Bookings on their own events.

    • EntertainmentProvider

      public EntertainmentProvider​(String orgName, String orgAddress, String paymentAccountEmail, String mainRepName, String mainRepEmail, String password, List<String> otherRepNames, List<String> otherRepEmails)
      Create a new EntertainmentProvider with an empty list of own events and a MockEntertainmentProviderSystem for their organisation.
      Parameters:
      orgName - name of the organisation for this account
      orgAddress - address of the organisation for this account
      paymentAccountEmail - email address corresponding to the EntertainmentProvider's account on the external PaymentSystem
      mainRepName - full name of the main representative of the organisation
      mainRepEmail - email address of the main representative of the organisation (used as the account email address)
      password - password for this account
      otherRepNames - list of full names of other representatives of the organisation
      otherRepEmails - list of emails of other representatives of the organisation
